[gd_scene load_steps=43 format=3]

; BOWSER — Final boss arena. Dark volcanic keep in a dimensional void.
; Palette: basalt + stone_dark + lava + fabric_red + gold + ember.
; Layout: approach causeway (stepping stones over lava pit) → octagonal
;   arena with 1m lava moat → central dais + throne backdrop.
; 13 enemies (2 chain-chomp stand-in bosses, 6 bobomb army, 2 piranha
;   elite guards, 2 goomba intro, 1 koopa), ~29 coins (20 yellow, 8 red,
;   1 blue), 1 star behind throne, 2 one-ups (pre-approach + chandelier),
;   metal cap in moat. Secrets: throne alcove, dungeon grate, chandelier.

